thread.title: John

author: John
title: John
text:
Just wanted to confirm what you probably already realise: you have a little star in your new girl Fenna. Very attractive to spend time with in all ways. Both interesting and interested as someone to converse with, and also interested in "the other thing"!!
In conversation she mentioned that she chose to work with you rather than another agency. That was a nice compliment for you as that agency is I guess 'the market leader'.
Anyhow I now know Fenna would have made an ideal dinner companion for Thursday, and indeed I would happily spend that time with her if possible. If not, Miranda has a lot to live up to ;)
